            "text": "by the much-frequented House,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4740,
            "text": "by the elevated canopy;",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4741,
            "text": "and by the swelling sea:",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4742,
            "text": "verily your Lord's chastisement shall come to pass,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4743,
            "text": "none can avert that.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4744,
            "text": "(It shall come to pass) on the Day when the heaven will convulse in a great convulsion,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4745,
            "text": "and the mountains shall violently fly about.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4746,
            "text": "Woe, then, on that Day to those who give the lie (to this Message)",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4747,
            "text": "and amuse themselves with vain argumentation.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4748,
            "text": "On the Day when they shall be thrust into Hell with a violent thrust (and shall be told):",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4749,
            "text": "“This is the Hell which you used to give the lie to.”",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4750,
            "text": "Is this, then, any feat of magic or are you unable to see?",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4751,
            "text": "Go now and burn in it. It is all the same whether you bear it patiently or do not bear it with patience. You are only being recompensed for your deeds.”",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4752,
            "text": "Surely the God-fearing shall be in Gardens and bliss,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4753,
            "text": "enjoying what Allah will have endowed them with; and their Lord will have saved them from the torment of the Blazing Fire.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4754,
            "text": "(They will be told): “Eat and drink to your hearts' content as a reward for your deeds.”",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4755,
            "text": "The God-fearing shall be reclining on couches facing each other, and We shall wed them to maidens with large, beautiful eyes.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4756,
            "text": "We shall unite the believers with those descendants of theirs who followed them in their faith, and shall not deny them any part of the reward for their good deeds. Every person is pledged to what he did.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4757,
            "text": "We shall provide them in abundance with all kinds of fruit and meat, whatever they may desire.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4758,
            "text": "They shall pass on to one another a cup that will incite neither levity nor sin.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4759,
            "text": "Youths as fair as hidden pearls will be set apart to wait upon them; they will be running to and fro to serve them.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4760,
            "text": "They will turn to one another and ask (regarding the past events).",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4761,
            "text": "They will say: “When we were living before among our kinsfolk we lived in constant fear (of Allah's displeasure).",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4762,
            "text": "Then Allah graced us with His favour and saved us from the chastisement of the scorching wind.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4763,
            "text": "Formerly we had always prayed to Him. Surely He is Most Benign, Most Compassionate.”",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4764,
            "text": "So exhort (them, O Prophet), for by your Lord's Grace, you are neither a soothsayer nor a madman.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4765,
            "text": "Or do they say: “He is a poet for whom we await an adverse turn of fortune.”",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4766,
            "text": "Tell them: “Wait; I too am waiting with you.”",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4767,
            "text": "Do their minds prompt them to say such things, or are they a people immersed in transgression?”",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4768,
            "text": "Do they say: “He has himself fabricated the Qur'an?” No; the truth is that they are altogether averse to believing.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4769,
            "text": "(If they are truthful in this), then let them produce a discourse of similar splendour.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4770,
            "text": "Did they come into being without any creator? Or were they their own creators?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4771,
            "text": "Or is it they who created the heavens and the earth? No; the truth is that they lack sure faith.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4772,
            "text": "Or do they have your Lord's treasures in their keeping? Or have absolute authority over them?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4773,
            "text": "Or do they have a ladder whereon they can climb and attempt to listen (to what is transpiring in the Higher Realm)? Then, let any of them who has listened to it produce a clear proof of it.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4774,
            "text": "Or does Allah have daughters whereas you have sons?",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4775,
            "text": "Or is it that you ask of them any recompense so that they should fear to be weighed down under the burden of debt?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4776,
            "text": "Or is it that they have access to (the Truths in) the realm beyond sense-perception which they are writing down?",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4777,
            "text": "Or are they contriving a stratagem against you? If so, that stratagem will rebound against the unbelievers.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4778,
            "text": "Do they have any god other than Allah? Exalted be Allah above whatever they associate (with Him in His Divinity).",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4779,
            "text": "(So obstinate are they that) even if they were to see some fragments of the sky falling down they would still say: “It is only a mass of cloud.”",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4780,
            "text": "So leave them alone until they encounter that Day of theirs when they shall be struck down,",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4781,
            "text": "when their stratagem shall be of no avail to them, nor shall they be succoured.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4782,
            "text": "Surely a chastisement awaits the wrong-doers even before the coming of that Day; but most of them do not know.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4783,
            "text": "Be patient, then, (O Prophet), until the judgement of your Lord comes. For surely you are before Our eyes. And celebrate the praise of your Lord when you rise,",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4784,
            "text": "and also celebrate His praise at night, and at the retreat of the stars.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 53,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النَّجۡمِ",
        "englishName": "An-Najm",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Star",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4785,
            "text": "By the star when it sets:",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4786,
            "text": "your companion has neither strayed nor is he deluded;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4787,
            "text": "nor does he speak out of his desire.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4788,
            "text": "This is nothing but a revelation that is conveyed to him,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4789,
            "text": "something that a very powerful one has imparted to him,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4790,
            "text": "one endowed with immense wisdom. He came forth and stood poised,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4791,
            "text": "being on the higher horizon.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4792,
            "text": "Then he drew near and hung above suspended,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4793,
            "text": "until he was two bows' length away, or nearer.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4794,
            "text": "Then he revealed to Allah's servant whatever he had to reveal.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4795,
            "text": "His heart added no untruth to what he saw.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4796,
            "text": "Are you, then, going to contend with him regarding what he sees with his eyes?",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4797,
            "text": "Indeed he saw him a second time,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4798,
            "text": "by the lote-tree at the farthest boundary,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4799,
            "text": "near which is the Garden of Abode.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4800,
            "text": "(This was) when the lote-tree was covered with that which covered it.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4801,
            "text": "His eye did not waver, nor did it stray,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4802,
            "text": "and he certainly saw some of the greatest Signs of His Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4803,
            "text": "Have you ever thought about al-Lat and al-Uzza,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4804,
            "text": "and about the third deity, al-Manat?",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4805,
            "text": "Shall you have the male issues, and He the female issues?",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4806,
            "text": "That is indeed an unfair division!",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4807,
            "text": "These are nothing but names that you and your forefathers have invented, for which Allah has sent down no authority. They are merely following their conjectures and their carnal desires although guidance has come to them from their Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4808,
            "text": "Does man imagine that whatever he wishes for is right for him?",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4809,
            "text": "To Allah belong both the Next World and the present.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4810,
            "text": "Numerous are the angels in the heavens; yet their intercession shall be of no avail, except in regard to those whom He grants the leave of intercession and whose plea He is pleased to accept.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4811,
            "text": "Those who do not believe in the Hereafter give angels the names of females,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4812,
            "text": "although they have no knowledge regarding that. They only follow their conjecture and conjecture can never take the place of the Truth.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4813,
            "text": "So leave alone those who turn away from the remembrance of Us and who seek nothing but the life of the world –",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4814,
            "text": "that being the utmost of their knowledge. Surely your Lord fully knows those who have strayed away from His Path and He also fully knows those who are rightly guided.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4815,
            "text": "To Allah alone belongs whatever is in the heavens and whatever is in the earth. He will requite the evil-doers for their deeds and bestow a goodly reward on those who have done good,",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4816,
            "text": "on those who avoid grave sins and shameful deeds, even if they may sometimes stumble into lesser offences. Surely your Lord is abounding in His Forgiveness. Very well is He aware of you since He produced you from the earth, and while you were still in your mothers' wombs and not yet born. So do not boastfully claim yourselves to be purified. He fully knows those that are truly Godfearing.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4817,
            "text": "(O Prophet), did you see him who turned away (from the Path of Allah),",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4818,
            "text": "who gave a little, and then stopped?",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4819,
            "text": "Does he have any knowledge of the world beyond the ken of sense-perception, and therefore, clearly sees (the Truth)?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4820,
            "text": "Has he not been informed of what is in the Scrolls of Moses,",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4821,
            "text": "and of Abraham, who lived up to the trust?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4822,
            "text": "“That no bearer of a burden shall bear the burden of another,",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4823,
            "text": "and that man shall have nothing but what he has striven for,",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4824,
            "text": "and that (the result of) his striving shall soon be seen,",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4825,
            "text": "and that he shall then be fully recompensed,",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4826,
            "text": "and that the final end is with your Lord,",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4827,
            "text": "and that He it is Who causes people to laugh and to cry,",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4828,
            "text": "and that He it is Who causes death and grants life,",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4829,
            "text": "and He it is Who created the two kinds, the male and the female,",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4830,
            "text": "from a drop of sperm when it was emitted,",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4831,
            "text": "and that it is for Him to grant the second life,",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4832,
            "text": "that He it is Who bestowed wealth and riches,",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4833,
            "text": "that He is the Lord of Sirius,",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4834,
            "text": "that He it is Who destroyed the ancient 'Ad,",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4835,
            "text": "and Thamud, leaving no trace of them,",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4836,
            "text": "and that He it is Who destroyed the people of Noah before for they were much given to iniquity and transgression.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4837,
            "text": "And He brought perdition upon the subverted cities",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4838,
            "text": "and caused them to be covered with that which He covered them with.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4839,
            "text": "So, which of your Lord's bounties will you doubt?”",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4840,
            "text": "This is a warning among the warnings of yore.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4841,
            "text": "The imminent Hour has drawn near,",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4842,
            "text": "and none but Allah can avert it.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4843,
            "text": "Will you, then, wonder at this?",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4844,
            "text": "Will you laugh at it rather than weep?",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4845,
            "text": "Will you occupy yourselves simply in merriment?",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4846,
            "text": "Prostrate yourselves before Allah, and serve Him.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": {
              "id": 13,
              "recommended": false,
              "obligatory": true
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 54,
        "name": "سُورَةُ القَمَرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Qamar",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Moon",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4847,
            "text": "The Hour of Resurrection drew near and the moon split asunder.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4848,
            "text": "(Regardless of any Signs these people see), they turn away and say: “This is an ongoing sorcery.”",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4849,
            "text": "They also gave the lie to (the splitting asunder of the moon) and only followed their desires. Yet everything is destined to reach an end.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4850,
            "text": "Surely there came to them narratives (of the ancient nations) that should suffice to deter (them from transgression),",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4851,
            "text": "narratives that are full of consummate wisdom. But warnings do not avail them.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4852,
            "text": "So turn away from them, (O Prophet). On the Day when a caller shall call them to a thing most terrible,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4853,
            "text": "with down-cast eyes they shall go forth from their graves, as though they were scattered locusts.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4854,
            "text": "They shall be hurrying forth towards the caller, and the unbelievers (who had once denied this Day), will say: “This is a woeful Day.”",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4855,
            "text": "Before them Noah's people also gave the lie (to his Message). They rejected Our servant as a liar, saying: “He is a madman”; and he was rebuffed.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4856,
            "text": "Then he called upon His Lord: “Verily I am vanquished; so come You to my aid.”",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4857,
            "text": "Thereupon We opened the gates of the sky for water to pour down,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4858,
            "text": "and We made the earth burst forth with springs, and all this water converged to fulfil that which had been decreed.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4859,
            "text": "And We bore Noah on the vessel built of planks and nails,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4860,
            "text": "which sailed on under Our supervision: a reward for him who had been shown ingratitude.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4861,
            "text": "And We left the Ark as a Sign. Is there, then, any who will take heed?",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4862,
            "text": "So how awesome were My chastisement and My warnings!",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4863,
            "text": "We have made this Qur'an easy as a reminder. Is there, then, any who will take heed?",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4864,
            "text": "'Ad also gave the lie (to Hud). So how awesome were My chastisement and My warnings!",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4865,
            "text": "We sent a tumultuous wind against them on a day of unremitting misfortune,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4866,
            "text": "which tore people away and hurled them as though they were trunks of uprooted palm-trees.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4867,
            "text": "So how awesome were My chastisement and My warnings!",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4868,
            "text": "We have made the Qur'an easy to derive lessons from. Is there, then, any who will take heed?",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4869,
            "text": "Thamud gave the lie to the warnings,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4870,
            "text": "saying: “Are we to follow a single mortal, one from among ourselves? If we do that, we shall surely be in error and folly.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4871,
            "text": "Was there none but he to whom the Reminder could be vouchsafed excluding all others? Nay; he is an insolent liar.”",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4872,
            "text": "(We told Our Messenger): “Tomorrow they shall know who is the insolent liar.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4873,
            "text": "We shall send the she-camel as a trial for them; so watch their end with patience.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4874,
            "text": "Let them know that the water should be divided between them and the she-camel, each availing their turn.”",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4875,
            "text": "Eventually, they summoned their companion, and he undertook the (outrageous) task and hamstrung the she-camel.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4876,
            "text": "So how awesome were My chastisement and My warnings!",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4877,
            "text": "Behold, We sent a single Blast against them, and they became like the trampled twigs of a sheep pen-builder.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4878,
            "text": "Surely We have made this Qur'an easy as a reminder. Is there, then, any who will take heed?",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4879,
            "text": "Lot's people also gave the lie to the warnings,",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4880,
            "text": "and behold, We let loose upon them a tempest which rained stones upon them, except upon Lot's household whom We rescued in the last hours of the night",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4881,
            "text": "as a favour from Us. Thus do We reward those who give thanks.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4882,
            "text": "Surely Lot warned his people that We shall seize them (with Our chastisement), but they doubted the warnings.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4883,
            "text": "Then they even solicited his guests from him, whereupon We blotted out their eyes, (telling them): “Now have a taste of My chastisement and My warnings.”",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4884,
            "text": "Indeed an abiding chastisement came upon them in the morning.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4885,
            "text": "So have a taste of My chastisement and My warnings.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4886,
            "text": "Surely We have made this Qur'an easy as a reminder. Is there, then, any who will take heed?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4887,
            "text": "Warnings also came to the Pharaonites,",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4888,
            "text": "but they gave the lie to Our Signs, to all of them. Thereupon We seized them with the seizing of the Most Mighty, the Most Powerful.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4889,
            "text": "Are your unbelievers (of Makkah) any better than they? Or have you been granted any immunity in the Scriptures?",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4890,
            "text": "Or do they say: “We are a strong legion, strong enough for victory?”",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4891,
            "text": "Soon shall this legion be routed and shall turn their backs and flee.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4892,
            "text": "Nay; the Hour of Doom is their appointed time, and the Hour shall be more calamitous and bitter.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4893,
            "text": "The evil-doers are victims of error and madness.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4894,
            "text": "There shall come a Day when they will be dragged on their faces into the Fire and will be told: “Now taste the flame of Hell.”",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4895,
            "text": "We have created everything in a determined measure.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4896,
            "text": "Our command consists of only one Word which is carried out in the twinkling of an eye.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4897,
            "text": "We did indeed destroy many like you. Is there, then, any who will heed?",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4898,
            "text": "All their deeds are recorded in the Scrolls;",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4899,
            "text": "everything large or small, is duly inscribed.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4900,
            "text": "Surely those who shun disobedience will dwell amidst Gardens and running streams",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4901,
            "text": "where they will be honourably seated in the presence of a King, Mighty in Power.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
