            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5274,
            "text": "and surely yours shall be a never-ending reward,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5275,
            "text": "and you are certainly on the most exalted standard of moral excellence.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5276,
            "text": "So you will soon see, and they too will see,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5277,
            "text": "which of you is afflicted with madness.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5278,
            "text": "Surely your Lord knows well those who have strayed from His Way just as He knows well those who are on the Right Way.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5279,
            "text": "Do not, then, yield to those who reject the Truth, decrying it as false;",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5280,
            "text": "they would wish you to be pliant so that they too may be pliant.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5281,
            "text": "And do not yield to any contemptible swearer,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5282,
            "text": "the fault-finder who goes around slandering,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5283,
            "text": "the hinderer of good, the transgressor, the sinful;",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5284,
            "text": "the coarse-grained, and above all mean and ignoble;",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5285,
            "text": "(who so acts) simply because he has wealth and sons,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5286,
            "text": "and whenever Our verses are rehearsed to him, he says: “These are fairy- tales of times gone by.”",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 564,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5287,
            "text": "Soon shall We brand him on his snout.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5288,
            "text": "We have put them [i.e., the Makkans] to test even as We put to test the owners of the orchard when they vowed that they would gather the fruit of their orchard in the morning,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5289,
            "text": "without making any allowance (for the will of Allah).",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5290,
            "text": "Thereupon a calamity from your Lord passed over it while they were asleep,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5291,
            "text": "and so by morning the orchard lay as though it had been fully harvested.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5292,
            "text": "At daybreak they called out to one another:",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5293,
            "text": "“Hurry to your orchard if you would gather its fruit.”",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5294,
            "text": "So off they went, whispering to one another:",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5295,
            "text": "“No destitute person shall enter it today.”",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5296,
            "text": "They went forth early, believing that they had the power (to gather the fruit).",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5297,
            "text": "But as soon as they beheld the orchard, (they cried out): “We have certainly lost the way;",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5298,
            "text": "rather, we are utterly ruined.”",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5299,
            "text": "The best among them said: “Did I not say to you: why do you not give glory to (your Lord)?”",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5300,
            "text": "They cried out: “Glory be to our Lord! Certainly we were sinners.”",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5301,
            "text": "Then they began to reproach one another.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5302,
            "text": "They said: “Woe to us! We had indeed transgressed.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5303,
            "text": "Maybe our Lord will give us a better orchard in its place; to our Lord do we penitently turn.”",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5304,
            "text": "Such is the chastisement; and the chastisement of the Hereafter is assuredly even greater, if only they knew.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 498,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5305,
            "text": "Surely the God-fearing shall have Gardens of bliss with their Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5306,
            "text": "What! Shall We treat those who have submitted (to Our command) like those who have acted as criminals?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5307,
            "text": "What is the matter with you? How ill do you judge!",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5308,
            "text": "Or do you have a Book wherein you read",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5309,
            "text": "that (in the Hereafter) you shall have all that you choose for yourselves?",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5310,
            "text": "Or have We sworn a covenant with you which We are bound to keep till the Day of Resurrection, (a covenant requiring that whatever you ordain for yourselves shall be yours)?",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5311,
            "text": "Ask them: “Which of them can guarantee that?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5312,
            "text": "Or has something been guaranteed by any of those whom they associate with Allah in His Divinity?” If so, let them bring forth their associates, if they are truthful.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5313,
            "text": "On the Day when the dreadful calamity will unfold, when people will be summoned to prostrate themselves, and yet they will not be able to prostrate.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 565,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5314,
            "text": "Their eyes shall be downcast and ignominy shall overwhelm them. For when they were safe and sound, they were summoned to prostrate themselves, (and they refused).",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5315,
            "text": "So leave Me, (O Prophet), to deal with him who gives the lie to this Discourse. We shall draw them little by little (to their undoing) in a way that they will not know.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5316,
            "text": "I am giving them a respite. Great is My scheme!",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5317,
            "text": "Or are you asking them for some compensation so that they feel burdened with debt?",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5318,
            "text": "Or do they have any knowledge of the Unseen which they are now writing down?",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5319,
            "text": "So bear with patience until the Judgement of your Lord comes, and do not belike the man in the fish (i.e., Jonah) who called out, choking with grief:",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5320,
            "text": "had his Lord not bestowed His favour upon him, he would have been cast upon that barren shore (and would have remained there) in disgrace.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5321,
            "text": "But his Lord exalted him, and included him among His righteous servants.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5322,
            "text": "When the unbelievers hear this Exhortation, they look at you as though they would knock you off your feet with their (hostile) glances. They say: “Surely he is afflicted with madness”;",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5323,
            "text": "although this is nothing but an Exhortation (to goodness) for everyone in the world.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 499,
            "hizbQuarter": 226,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 69,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الحَاقَّةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Haaqqa",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Reality",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5324,
            "text": "The indubitable event!",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5325,
            "text": "And what is that indubitable event?",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5326,
            "text": "And what do you know what that indubitable event is?",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5327,
            "text": "The Thamud and the Ad denied the (possibility of a) sudden calamity, calling it false.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5328,
            "text": "Then the Thamud were destroyed by an awesome upheaval;",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5329,
            "text": "and the Ad were destroyed by a furiously raging wind-storm",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5330,
            "text": "which He let loose upon them for seven nights and eight days in succession; so that (if you had been there) you might have seen people lying prostrate, as though they were uprooted trunks of hollowed palm trees.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5331,
            "text": "Do you now see any trace of them?",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 566,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5332,
            "text": "Pharaoh and those before him and the people of the overturned habitations all engaged in the same great sin.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5333,
            "text": "They did not follow the Messenger of their Lord, and so He seized them with a severe grip.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5334,
            "text": "Verily when the water rose to great heights, We bore you upon a floating vessel (i.e. the Ark)",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5335,
            "text": "so that We might make it an instructive event for you, and retentive ears might preserve its memory.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5336,
            "text": "So when the Trumpet is blown with a single blast",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5337,
            "text": "and the earth and the mountains are carried aloft and are crushed to bits at one stroke,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5338,
            "text": "on that Day shall that indubitable event come to pass;",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5339,
            "text": "when the sky will be rent asunder, the grip holding it together having loosened on that Day,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5340,
            "text": "and the angels will stand on the sides, with eight of them bearing aloft the Throne of your Lord on that Day.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5341,
            "text": "That will be the Day when you shall be brought forth (before Allah) and no secret of yours shall remain hidden.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5342,
            "text": "On that Day, he whose Record is given to him in his right hand will say: “Lo! Read my Record!",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5343,
            "text": "Verily I was sure that I would be handed over my account.”",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5344,
            "text": "Then he shall find himself in a life of bliss;",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5345,
            "text": "in a lofty Garden",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5346,
            "text": "the clusters of whose fruit will be hanging low to be within reach (of the inmates of Paradise).",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5347,
            "text": "(They will be told): “Eat and drink with good cheer as a reward for the good deeds you did in the days that have passed by.”",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5348,
            "text": "As for him whose Record will be given to him in his left hand, he will exclaim: “Would that I had never been given my Record,",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5349,
            "text": "and had not known my account.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5350,
            "text": "Oh! Would that the death that came to me in the world had made an end of me!",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5351,
            "text": "My riches have not availed me,",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5352,
            "text": "and my authority has vanished.”",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5353,
            "text": "(A command will be issued): “Seize him and shackle him,",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5354,
            "text": "then cast him in the Fire,",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5355,
            "text": "then fasten him with a chain, seventy cubits long.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5356,
            "text": "He would not believe in Allah, the Most Great;",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5357,
            "text": "nor would he urge the feeding of the poor.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 567,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5358,
            "text": "Today he has been left here friendless;",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5359,
            "text": "and has no food except the filth from the washing of wounds,",
