            "text": "which only the sinners will eat.”",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 500,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5361,
            "text": "But no; I swear by what you see,",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5362,
            "text": "and by what you do not see,",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5363,
            "text": "that this is the speech of an honourable Messenger,",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5364,
            "text": "not the speech of a poet. Little do you believe!",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5365,
            "text": "Nor is this the speech of a soothsayer. Little do you reflect!",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5366,
            "text": "It has been revealed by the Lord of the Universe.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5367,
            "text": "And if he [i.e., the Prophets] had forged this Discourse and thereafter ascribed it to Us,",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5368,
            "text": "We would surely have seized him by the right hand,",
