            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5369,
            "text": "and then severed his life vein;",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5370,
            "text": "and not one of you would have been able to withhold Us from doing so.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5371,
            "text": "Surely it is a Good Counsel for the God-fearing.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5372,
            "text": "We certainly know that some among you will give the lie to it,",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5373,
            "text": "and surely it will be a cause of regret for the unbelievers.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5374,
            "text": "Certainly it is a Truth of absolute certainty.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 501,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5375,
            "text": "So glorify the name of your Lord Most Great.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
