            "text": "O you enveloped in your cloak!",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5497,
            "text": "Arise, and warn,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5498,
            "text": "and magnify the glory of your Lord,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5499,
            "text": "and purify your robes,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5500,
            "text": "and shun uncleanness,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5501,
            "text": "and bestow not favour in order to seek from others a greater return,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5502,
            "text": "and persevere for your Lord's sake.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5503,
            "text": "When the Trumpet shall be sounded,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5504,
            "text": "that will surely be a hard day,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5505,
            "text": "not an easy day for the unbelievers.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5506,
            "text": "Leave Me with him whom I alone have created,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5507,
            "text": "whom I have endowed with abundant riches,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5508,
            "text": "and sons ever present with him,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5509,
            "text": "and for whom I have smoothed the way (to power and riches),",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5510,
            "text": "and who still greedily desires that I should bestow upon him more.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5511,
            "text": "By no means; he is stubbornly opposed to Our Signs.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5512,
            "text": "I shall soon constrain him to a hard ascent.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5513,
            "text": "He reflected and then hatched a scheme.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5514,
            "text": "Ruin seize him, how did he hatch a scheme?",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5515,
            "text": "Again, ruin seize him, how did he hatch a scheme?",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5516,
            "text": "He looked (at others);",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5517,
            "text": "then frowned and scowled;",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5518,
            "text": "then he retreated and waxed proud,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5519,
            "text": "and said: “This (Qur'an) is merely a sorcery of yore;",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5520,
            "text": "this is nothing but the word of a mere mortal!”",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5521,
            "text": "Him shall I soon roast in Hell.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5522,
            "text": "And what do you know what Hell is?",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5523,
            "text": "It spares nothing; it leaves nothing intact;",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5524,
            "text": "it scorches (even) the skin.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5525,
            "text": "Over it are nineteen keepers.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5526,
            "text": "We have appointed none but angels as the keepers of the Fire, and We have not made their number but as a trial for the unbelievers so that those who have been endowed with the Book will be convinced and the believers' faith will increase, and neither those who have been endowed with the Book nor the believers will fall into any doubt. As for those in whose hearts there is a sickness as well as the unbelievers, they will say: “What did Allah aim at by this strange parable?” Thus does Allah let whomsoever He pleases to go astray, and directs whomsoever He pleases to the Right Way. And none knows the hosts of your Lord but He. (And Hell has only been mentioned here) that people may take heed.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5527,
            "text": "Nay, by the moon,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5528,
            "text": "and by the night when it recedes,",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5529,
            "text": "and by the day when it dawns (with its radiance),",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5530,
            "text": "surely (Hell) is one of the greatest Signs,",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5531,
            "text": "a warning to humankind,",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5532,
            "text": "a warning to everyone of you whether he would like to come forward or lag behind.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5533,
            "text": "Each one is a hostage to one's deeds,",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5534,
            "text": "save the People of the Right Hand",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5535,
            "text": "who shall be in the Gardens, and shall ask",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5536,
            "text": "about the guilty ones:",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5537,
            "text": "“What drove you to Hell?”",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5538,
            "text": "They will answer: “We were not among those who observed Prayer,",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5539,
            "text": "and we did not feed the poor,",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5540,
            "text": "and we indulged in vain talk with those who indulged in vain talk,",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5541,
            "text": "and we gave the lie to the Day of Judgement",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5542,
            "text": "until the inevitable event overtook us.”",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5543,
            "text": "The intercession of the intercessors shall then be of no avail to them.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5544,
            "text": "What is the matter with people that they are turning away from this Exhortation,",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5545,
            "text": "as though they were frightened wild asses,",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5546,
            "text": "fleeing from a lion?",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5547,
            "text": "No indeed; each one of them desires that open letters be sent to each of them.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5548,
            "text": "No indeed; the truth is that they have no fear of the Hereafter.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5549,
            "text": "Nay; this is an Exhortation.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5550,
            "text": "So, whoever wills may benefit from it.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5551,
            "text": "But they will not benefit from it unless Allah Himself so wills. He is worthy to be feared; and He is worthy to forgive (those that fear Him).",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 75,
        "name": "سُورَةُ القِيَامَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Qiyaama",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Resurrection",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5552,
            "text": "Nay, I swear by the Day of Resurrection;",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5553,
            "text": "and nay, I swear by the self-reproaching soul!",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5554,
            "text": "Does man imagine that We will not be able to bring his bones together again?",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5555,
            "text": "Yes indeed; We have the power to remould even his finger-tips.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5556,
            "text": "But man desires to persist in his evil ways.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5557,
            "text": "He asks: “When will the Day of Resurrection be?”",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5558,
            "text": "When the sight is dazed,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5559,
            "text": "and the moon is eclipsed,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5560,
            "text": "and the sun and the moon are joined together,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5561,
            "text": "on that Day will man say: “Whither the refuge?”",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5562,
            "text": "No, there is no refuge.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5563,
            "text": "With your Lord alone will be the retreat that Day.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5564,
            "text": "On that Day will man be apprised of his deeds, both the earlier and the later.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5565,
            "text": "But lo, man is well aware of himself,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5566,
            "text": "even though he might make up excuses.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5567,
            "text": "(O Prophet), do not stir your tongue hastily (to commit the Revelation to memory).",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5568,
            "text": "Surely it is for Us to have you commit it to memory and to recite it.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5569,
            "text": "And so when We recite it, follow its recitation attentively;",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5570,
            "text": "then it will be for Us to explain it.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5571,
            "text": "Nay; the truth is that you love ardently (the good of this world) that can be obtained hastily,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5572,
            "text": "and are oblivious of the Hereafter.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5573,
            "text": "Some faces on that Day will be fresh and resplendent,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5574,
            "text": "and will be looking towards their Lord;",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5575,
            "text": "and some faces on that Day will be gloomy,",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5576,
            "text": "believing that a crushing calamity is about to strike them.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5577,
            "text": "Nay; when a man's soul reaches up to the throat,",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5578,
            "text": "and it is said: “Is there any enchanter who can step forward and help (by his chanting)?”",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5579,
            "text": "and he realises that the hour of parting is come,",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5580,
            "text": "and calf is inter-twined with calf.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5581,
            "text": "On that Day you will be driven to your Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5582,
            "text": "But he did not verify the Truth, nor did he observe Prayer;",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5583,
            "text": "on the contrary, he gave the lie to the Truth and turned his back upon it,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5584,
            "text": "then he went back to his kinsfolk, elated with pride.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5585,
            "text": "This (attitude) is worthy of you, altogether worthy;",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5586,
            "text": "again, it is worthy of you, altogether worthy.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5587,
            "text": "Does man think that he will be left alone, unquestioned?",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5588,
            "text": "Was he not a drop of ejaculated semen,",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5589,
            "text": "then he became a clot, and then Allah made it into a living body and proportioned its parts,",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5590,
            "text": "and then He made of him a pair, male and female?",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5591,
            "text": "Does He, then, not have the power to bring back the dead to life?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 76,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الإِنسَانِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Insaan",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Man",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5592,
            "text": "Was there a period of time when man was not even worthy of a mention?",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5593,
            "text": "Verily We created man out of a drop of intermingled sperm so that We might try him, and We therefore endowed him with hearing and sight.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5594,
            "text": "Surely We showed him the Right Path, regardless of whether he chooses to be thankful or unthankful (to his Lord).",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5595,
            "text": "For the unbelievers, We have kept ready chains and fetters and a Blazing Fire.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5596,
            "text": "The virtuous shall drink from a cup tempered with camphor water.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5597,
            "text": "This will be a gushing spring wherefrom Allah's servants shall drink wine, a spring from which they will take out channels wherever they wish.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5598,
            "text": "These will be the ones who fulfil their vows and dread the Day whose woe shall be spread far and wide;",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5599,
            "text": "those who, for the love of Him, feed the needy, and the orphan, and the captive,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5600,
            "text": "(saying): “We feed you only for Allah's sake; we do not seek of you any recompense or thanks,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5601,
            "text": "we fear from our Lord a Day that shall be long and distressful.”",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5602,
            "text": "So Allah shall guard them against the woe of that Day, and will procure them freshness and joy,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5603,
            "text": "and will reward them for their steadfastness with Paradise and robes of silk.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5604,
            "text": "There they will recline on elevated couches and will be subjected neither to the burning heat of the sun nor to bitter cold.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5605,
            "text": "The shades of Paradise will bend over them, and its fruits will be brought within their easy reach;",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5606,
            "text": "and there shall be passed around them vessels of silver and goblets of crystal,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5607,
            "text": "goblets bright as crystal but made of silver, filled to exact measure.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5608,
            "text": "Therein they shall be served a cup flavoured with ginger,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5609,
            "text": "drawn from a spring (in Paradise) called Salsabil.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5610,
            "text": "There boys of everlasting youth shall go about attending them: when you see them, you would think that they are scattered pearls.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5611,
            "text": "Whitherto you look around, you will see an abundance of bliss and the glories of a great kingdom.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5612,
            "text": "They [i.e., the virtuous] shall be attired in garments of fine green silk and rich brocade and will be adorned with bracelets of silver. Their Lord will give them a pure wine to drink.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5613,
            "text": "Behold, this is your recompense and your endeavour has been appreciated.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5614,
            "text": "(O Prophet), indeed We have revealed the Qur'an to you in portions.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5615,
            "text": "So persevere with the command of your Lord and do not pay any heed to the wicked and the unbelieving,",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5616,
            "text": "and remember the name of your Lord, morning and evening;",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5617,
            "text": "and prostrate yourself before Him at night, and extol His Glory during the long watches of the night.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5618,
            "text": "Verily they love (the good of this world) that is hastily obtainable and are oblivious of the burdensome Day ahead of them.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5619,
            "text": "We created them and strengthened their joints; and whenever We wish, We can change their faces entirely.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5620,
            "text": "Verily this is an Exhortation; so let him who so will take a way to his Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5621,
            "text": "But your willing shall be of no avail until Allah Himself so wills. Surely Allah is All-Knowing, Most Wise.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5622,
            "text": "He admits to His Mercy whomsoever He pleases. As for the wrong-doers, He has prepared for them a grievous chastisement.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 77,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُرۡسَلَاتِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Mursalaat",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Emissaries",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5623,
            "text": "By the (winds) sent forth in quick succession,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5624,
            "text": "which then blow tempestuously",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5625,
            "text": "and raise (clouds) and scatter them around,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5626,
            "text": "then winnow them thoroughly,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5627,
            "text": "and then cast (Allah's) remembrance (in people's hearts),",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5628,
            "text": "to serve as an excuse or a warning.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5629,
            "text": "Surely what you are promised shall come to pass.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5630,
            "text": "So when the stars are extinguished,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5631,
            "text": "and the sky is rent asunder,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5632,
            "text": "and the mountains are blown away,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5633,
            "text": "and the appointed time to bring the Messengers together arrives, (then shall the promised event come to pass).",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5634,
            "text": "To which Day has this task been deferred?",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5635,
            "text": "To the Day of Judgement.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5636,
            "text": "What do you know what the Day of Judgement is?",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5637,
            "text": "Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth!",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5638,
            "text": "Did We not destroy many a nation of the earlier times?",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5639,
            "text": "And We shall cause those of later times to follow them.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5640,
            "text": "Thus do We deal with the guilty.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5641,
            "text": "Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth!",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5642,
            "text": "Did We not create you of a mean fluid,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5643,
            "text": "which We then placed in a secure repository",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5644,
            "text": "until an appointed time?",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5645,
            "text": "See that We had the power to do so. Great indeed is Our power to do what We will.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5646,
            "text": "Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth!",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5647,
            "text": "Did We not make the earth a receptacle,",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
