            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5656,
            "text": "Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth!",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5657,
            "text": "That will be the Day on which they will not (be able to) utter a word,",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5658,
            "text": "nor will they be allowed to proffer excuses.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5659,
            "text": "Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth!",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5660,
            "text": "That is the Day of Judgement on which We have assembled you as well as all those who went before you.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5661,
            "text": "So if you have any ploy, try it against Me!",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5662,
            "text": "Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth!",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
