            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5668,
            "text": "Eat and enjoy yourselves for a while. Surely you are evil-doers.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5669,
            "text": "Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth!",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5670,
            "text": "When it is said to them: “Bow down (before Allah),” they do not bow down.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5671,
            "text": "Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth!",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
