            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5689,
            "text": "Surely the Day of Judgement has an appointed time;",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5690,
            "text": "the Day when the Trumpet shall be blown, and you will come forth in multitudes;",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5691,
            "text": "and when the sky shall be opened up and will become all doors;",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5692,
            "text": "and the mountains will be set in motion and become a mirage.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5693,
            "text": "Surely the Hell is an ambush,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5694,
            "text": "a resort for the rebellious;",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5695,
            "text": "therein they shall abide for ages,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5696,
            "text": "they shall taste in it no coolness, nor any pleasant drink",
