            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5697,
            "text": "save boiling water and wash of the wounds;",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5698,
            "text": "a befitting recompense for their deeds.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5699,
            "text": "For indeed they did not look forward to any reckoning,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5700,
            "text": "and roundly denied Our Signs as false.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5701,
            "text": "And everything have We recorded in a Book.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5702,
            "text": "So taste (the fruit of your deeds). We shall only increase your torment.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5703,
            "text": "Surely the state of triumph awaits the God-fearing:",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5704,
            "text": "gardens and vineyards,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5705,
            "text": "and youthful maidens of like age,",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5706,
            "text": "and an overflowing cup.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5707,
            "text": "Therein they shall hear no idle talk, nor any falsehood;",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5708,
            "text": "a recompense from your Lord and an ample reward",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5709,
            "text": "from the Lord of the heavens and the earth and of that which is between them; the Most Merciful Lord before Whom none dare utter a word.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5710,
            "text": "The Day when the Spirit and the angels are ranged row on row. None shall speak save he whom the Merciful Lord will permit; and he too will speak what is right.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5711,
            "text": "That Day is sure to come. So let him who will seek a resort with his Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5712,
            "text": "Lo! We warn you of a chastisement near at hand; the Day when a man will look on what his own hands have sent forth, and the unbelievers shall say: “Oh would that I were utter dust.”",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 79,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النَّازِعَاتِ",
