            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5717,
            "text": "and then manage the affairs of the Universe (according to their Lord's commands).",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5718,
            "text": "The Day when the quaking will cause a violent convulsion,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5719,
            "text": "and will be followed by another quaking.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5720,
            "text": "On that Day some hearts shall tremble (with fright),",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5721,
            "text": "and their eyes shall be downcast with dread.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5722,
            "text": "They say: “Shall we indeed be restored to life,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5723,
            "text": "even after we have been reduced to bones, hollow and rotten?”",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5724,
            "text": "They say: “That will then be a return with a great loss!”",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5725,
            "text": "Surely they will need no more than a single stern blast,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5726,
            "text": "and lo, they will all be in the open plain.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5727,
            "text": "Has Moses' story reached you?",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5728,
            "text": "When his Lord called him in the sacred valley of Tuwa,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5729,
            "text": "and directed him: “Go to Pharaoh, he has rebelled,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5730,
            "text": "and say to him: 'Are you willing to be purified,",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5731,
            "text": "that I may direct you to your Lord and then you hold Him in awe?'”",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5732,
            "text": "Then Moses (went to Pharaoh and) showed him the Great Sign;",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5733,
            "text": "but he denied it as false and disobeyed,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5734,
            "text": "and then he turned back to have recourse to his craftiness,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5735,
            "text": "and gathered his people and declared:",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5736,
            "text": "“I am the supreme lord of you all.”",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5737,
            "text": "Thereupon Allah seized him for the chastisement of the World to Come as well as of the present.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5738,
            "text": "Surely there is a great lesson in it for whoever would fear (Allah).",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5739,
            "text": "Is it harder to create you or the heaven? But Allah built it,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5740,
            "text": "and raised its vault high and proportioned it;",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5741,
            "text": "and covered its night with darkness and brought forth from it its day;",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5742,
            "text": "and thereafter spread out the earth,",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5743,
            "text": "and brought out of it its water and its pasture,",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5744,
            "text": "and firmly fixed in it mountains;",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5745,
            "text": "all this as provision for you and your cattle.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5746,
            "text": "But when the great calamity will come about",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5747,
            "text": "on the Day when man will recall all his strivings,",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5748,
            "text": "and Hell will be brought in sight for anyone to see:",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5749,
            "text": "then he who transgressed",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5750,
            "text": "and preferred the life of this world,",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5751,
            "text": "most surely his abode shall be Hell.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5752,
            "text": "But he who feared to stand before his Lord, and restrained himself from evil desires,",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5753,
            "text": "most surely his abode shall be Paradise.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5754,
            "text": "They ask you about the Hour: “When will it be?”",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5755,
            "text": "What concern do you have to speak about that?",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5756,
            "text": "Its knowledge rests with your Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5757,
            "text": "You are only a warner to him who has a fear of it.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5758,
            "text": "On the Day they see it, they will feel as though they had stayed (in the grave) no more than one evening or one morning.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
