            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5807,
            "text": "when the souls shall be rejoined (with their bodies),",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5808,
            "text": "and when the girl-child buried alive shall be asked:",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5809,
            "text": "for what offence was she killed?",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5810,
            "text": "and when the scrolls of (men's) deeds shall be unfolded,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5811,
            "text": "and when Heaven is laid bare;",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5812,
            "text": "and Hell is stoked,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5813,
            "text": "and Paradise brought nigh:",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5814,
            "text": "then shall each person know what he has brought along.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5815,
            "text": "No indeed; I swear by the alternating stars",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5816,
            "text": "that hide,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5817,
            "text": "and by the night as it recedes,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5818,
            "text": "and the morn as it breathes.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5819,
            "text": "Verily this is the word of a noble message-bearer;",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5820,
            "text": "one mighty and held in honour with the Lord of the Throne;",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5821,
            "text": "there he is obeyed and held trustworthy.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5822,
            "text": "(O people of Makkah), your companion is not mad;",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5823,
            "text": "he indeed saw the message-bearer on the clear horizon;",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5824,
            "text": "nor does he grudge (conveying this knowledge about) the Unseen;",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5825,
            "text": "nor is it a word of an accursed Satan.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5826,
            "text": "Where to are you then heading?",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5827,
            "text": "It is nothing but Good Counsel for everyone in the world,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5828,
            "text": "for everyone of you who wishes to follow the Straight Way;",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5829,
            "text": "but your wishing will not avail unless Allah, the Lord of the Universe, so wishes.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 586,
            "ruku": 523,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 82,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الانفِطَارِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Infitaar",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Cleaving",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5830,
            "text": "When the heaven is split asunder,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5831,
            "text": "when the stars are scattered,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5832,
            "text": "when the seas are made to burst forth,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5833,
            "text": "and when graves are laid open,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5834,
            "text": "everyone shall know all his deeds, both the earlier and the later.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5835,
            "text": "O man! What has deceived you about your generous Lord",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5836,
            "text": "Who created you, shaped you, and made you well-proportioned,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5837,
            "text": "and set you in whatever form He pleased?",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5838,
            "text": "No indeed; (the fact is that) you deny the Reckoning, declaring it a lie;",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5839,
            "text": "you do so the while there are watchers over you;",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5840,
            "text": "noble scribes,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5841,
            "text": "who know what you do.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5842,
            "text": "Surely the virtuous shall be in Bliss,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5843,
            "text": "and the wicked shall be in the Blazing Fire.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5844,
            "text": "They shall enter it on the Day of Recompense",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5845,
            "text": "and then shall never come out of it.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5846,
            "text": "What do you know what the Day of Recompense is?",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5847,
            "text": "Again, what do you know what the Day of Recompense is?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5848,
            "text": "It is the Day when no one shall have the power to do anything for another, and all command shall be Allah's.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 83,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُطَفِّفِينَ",
        "englishName": "Al-Mutaffifin",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Defrauding",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5849,
            "text": "Woe to the stinters;",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5850,
            "text": "those who, when they take from others by measure, take their full share;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5851,
            "text": "but who, when they measure or weigh for others, give less than their due.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5852,
            "text": "Do they not realise that they will be raised to life",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5853,
            "text": "on a Great Day,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5854,
            "text": "a Day when mankind will stand before the Lord of the Universe?",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5855,
            "text": "No indeed! Verily the deeds of the wicked are in the Record locked up in the prison-house!",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5856,
            "text": "And how would you know what the Record of the prison-house is?",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5857,
            "text": "It is a Book inscribed.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5858,
            "text": "Woe, then, to those that give the lie,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5859,
            "text": "those that give the lie to the Day of Recompense.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5860,
            "text": "Yet none gives the lie to it except the transgressor immersed in sin;",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5861,
            "text": "who, when Our verses are recited to him, says: “Mere tales of olden times!”",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5862,
            "text": "No indeed! The truth is that their hearts have become rusted on account of their evil deeds.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5863,
            "text": "No indeed! On that Day they will be screened off from seeing their Lord,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5864,
            "text": "and then they shall enter Hell,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5865,
            "text": "whereafter they will be told: “This is what you used to give the lie to.”",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5866,
            "text": "No indeed! Verily, the deeds of the virtuous shall be in the record of the exalted ones.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5867,
            "text": "And what do you know what the Record of the exalted ones is?",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5868,
            "text": "It is a Book inscribed,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5869,
            "text": "which the angels placed near Allah to safeguard.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5870,
            "text": "Verily the virtuous shall be in Bliss;",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5871,
            "text": "resting on couches, looking around.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5872,
            "text": "You shall see upon their faces the glow of bliss.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5873,
            "text": "They will be served a drink of the finest sealed wine,",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5874,
            "text": "whose seal is musk – so let all aspirants aspire after that –",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
