        "name": "سُورَةُ الأَعۡلَىٰ",
        "englishName": "Al-A'laa",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Most High",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5949,
            "text": "Glorify the name of your Lord, the Most High,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5950,
            "text": "Who created all things and fashioned them in good proportion;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5951,
            "text": "Who determined and guided them,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5952,
            "text": "Who brought forth the pasture,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5953,
            "text": "and then made it into a blackish straw.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5954,
            "text": "We shall make you recite and then you will not forget,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5955,
            "text": "except what Allah should wish. He knows all that is manifest and all that is hidden.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5956,
            "text": "We shall ease you to follow the way of Ease.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5957,
            "text": "So render good counsel if good counsel will avail.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5958,
            "text": "He who fears (Allah) shall heed it,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5959,
            "text": "but the wretched will turn away from it.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5960,
            "text": "He will be cast into the Great Fire.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5961,
            "text": "Then he will neither die in it, nor live.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5962,
            "text": "He who purified himself shall prosper,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5963,
            "text": "remembering his Lord's name and praying.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5964,
            "text": "No; but you prefer the present life,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5965,
            "text": "whereas the Hereafter is better and more enduring.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5966,
            "text": "This, indeed, was in the ancient Scrolls,",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5967,
            "text": "the Scrolls of Abraham and Moses.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 88,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الغَاشِيَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Ghaashiya",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Overwhelming",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5968,
            "text": "Has the news of the overwhelming event reached you?",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5969,
            "text": "Some faces that Day shall be downcast with fear,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5970,
            "text": "be toiling and worn-out;",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5971,
            "text": "they shall burn in a Scorching Fire;",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5972,
            "text": "their drink shall be from a boiling spring.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5973,
            "text": "They shall have no food except bitter dry thorns",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5974,
            "text": "that will neither nourish nor satisfy their hunger.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5975,
            "text": "On that very Day some faces shall be radiant with joy,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5976,
            "text": "well-pleased with their striving.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5977,
            "text": "They will be in a lofty Garden",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5978,
            "text": "wherein they shall hear no vain talk.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5979,
            "text": "In it there shall be a flowing spring,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5980,
            "text": "and couches raised high,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5981,
            "text": "and goblets laid out,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5982,
            "text": "and cushions arrayed in rows,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5983,
            "text": "and rich carpets levelled out.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5984,
            "text": "Do (these unbelievers) not observe the camels: how they were created?",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5985,
            "text": "And the sky: how it was raised high?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5986,
            "text": "And the mountains: how they were fixed?",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5987,
            "text": "And the earth: how it was spread out?",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5988,
            "text": "So render good counsel, for you are simply required to counsel,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5989,
            "text": "and are not invested with the authority to compel them.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5990,
            "text": "But whoever will turn away (from the Truth),",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5991,
            "text": "Allah will chastise him with the most terrible chastisement.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5992,
            "text": "Surely to Us is their return;",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5993,
            "text": "and then it is for Us to call them to account.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 89,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الفَجۡرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Fajr",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Dawn",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5994,
            "text": "By the dawn,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5995,
            "text": "and the ten nights,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5996,
            "text": "and the even and the odd,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5997,
            "text": "and by the night when it departs.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5998,
            "text": "Is there in this an oath for one endowed with understanding?",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5999,
            "text": "Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with Ad",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6000,
            "text": "of Iram, known for their lofty columns,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6001,
            "text": "the like of whom no nation was ever created in the lands of the world?",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6002,
            "text": "And how did He deal with Thamud who hewed out rocks in the valley?",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6003,
            "text": "And with Pharaoh of the tent pegs",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6004,
            "text": "who transgressed in the countries of the world",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6005,
            "text": "spreading in them much corruption?",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6006,
            "text": "Then their Lord unloosed upon them the lash of chastisement.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6007,
            "text": "Truly your Lord is ever watchful.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6008,
            "text": "As for man, when his Lord tests him by exalting him and bestowing His bounties upon him, he says: “My Lord has exalted me.”",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6009,
            "text": "But when He tests him by straitening his sustenance, he says: “My Lord has humiliated me.”",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6010,
            "text": "But no; you do not treat the orphan honourably,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6011,
            "text": "and do not urge one another to feed the poor,",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6012,
            "text": "and greedily devour the entire inheritance,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6013,
            "text": "and love the riches, loving them ardently.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6014,
            "text": "But no; when the earth is ground to powder,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6015,
            "text": "and when your Lord appears with rows upon rows of angels,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6016,
            "text": "and when Hell is brought near that Day. On that Day will man understand, but of what avail will that understanding be?",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6017,
            "text": "He will say: “Would that I had sent ahead what would be of avail for this life of mine!”",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6018,
            "text": "Then on that Day Allah will chastise as none other can chastise;",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6019,
            "text": "and Allah will bind as none other can bind.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6020,
            "text": "(On the other hand it will be said): “O serene soul!",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6021,
            "text": "Return to your Lord well-pleased (with your blissful destination), well-pleasing (to your Lord).",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6022,
            "text": "So enter among My (righteous) servants",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6023,
            "text": "and enter My Paradise.”",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 90,
        "name": "سُورَةُ البَلَدِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Balad",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The City",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6024,
            "text": "Nay! I swear by this city",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6025,
            "text": "– this city wherein you have been rendered violable–",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6026,
            "text": "and I swear by the parent and his offspring:",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6027,
            "text": "Verily We have created man into toil and hardship.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6028,
            "text": "Does he think that no one can overpower him?",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6029,
            "text": "He says: “I have squandered enormous wealth.”",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6030,
            "text": "Does he believe that none has seen him?",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6031,
            "text": "Did We not grant him two eyes,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6032,
            "text": "and a tongue and two lips?",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6033,
            "text": "And did We not show him the two highroads (of good and evil)?",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6034,
            "text": "But he did not venture to scale the difficult steep.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6035,
            "text": "And what do you know what that difficult steep is?",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6036,
            "text": "It is freeing someone's neck from slavery;",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6037,
            "text": "or giving food on a day of hunger",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6038,
            "text": "to an orphan near of kin;",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6039,
            "text": "or to a destitute lying in dust;",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6040,
            "text": "and, then besides this, he be one of those who believed, and enjoined upon one another steadfastness and enjoined upon one another compassion.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6041,
            "text": "These are the People of the Right Hand.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6042,
            "text": "As for those who rejected Our Signs, they are the People of the Left Hand.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6043,
            "text": "Upon them shall be a Fire that will hem them in.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 91,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الشَّمۡسِ",
        "englishName": "Ash-Shams",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Sun",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6044,
            "text": "By the sun and its heat and brightness,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6045,
            "text": "and by the moon as it follows it;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6046,
            "text": "and by the day as it displays the sun's glory,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6047,
            "text": "and by the night as it envelopes the sun;",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6048,
            "text": "and by the sky and by Him Who made it;",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6049,
            "text": "and by the earth and by Him Who stretched it out;",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6050,
            "text": "and by the soul and by Him Who perfectly proportioned it,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6051,
            "text": "and imbued it with (the consciousness of) its evil and its piety:",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6052,
            "text": "He who purifies it will prosper,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6053,
            "text": "and he who suppresses it will be ruined.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6054,
            "text": "In their presumptuous insolence the Thamud called the Truth a lie",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6055,
            "text": "when their arch-criminal rose up in rage.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6056,
            "text": "Then Allah's Messenger warned them: “Hands off the she-camel and her drink!”",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6057,
            "text": "But they rejected his statement as a lie and hamstrung the she-camel. For that crime their Lord rumbled down upon them, utterly razing them to the ground.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6058,
            "text": "He has no fear of its sequel.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 92,
        "name": "سُورَةُ اللَّيۡلِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Lail",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Night",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6059,
            "text": "By the night when it enshrouds,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6060,
            "text": "and by the day when it breaks in its glory,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6061,
            "text": "and by Him Who created the male and the female:",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6062,
            "text": "surely your strivings are divergent.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6063,
            "text": "As for him who gave out his wealth (for Allah's sake) and abstained (from disobeying Him),",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6064,
            "text": "and affirmed the Truth of goodness:",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6065,
            "text": "We shall facilitate for him the Way to Bliss.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6066,
            "text": "As for him who was a miser and behaved with aversion (to Allah),",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6067,
            "text": "and denied the Truth of goodness:",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6068,
            "text": "We shall facilitate for him the way to Hardship,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6069,
            "text": "and his wealth shall be of no avail to him when he perishes.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6070,
            "text": "Surely it is for Us to show the Right Way,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6071,
            "text": "and to Us belong the Next Life and the present.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6072,
            "text": "I have now warned you of a Blazing Fire,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6073,
            "text": "where none shall burn except the most wicked,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6074,
            "text": "who rejected the Truth, calling it falsehood and turned his back on it.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6075,
            "text": "But the God-fearing shall be kept away from it,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6076,
            "text": "the Godfearing who spends his wealth to purify himself;",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6077,
            "text": "not as payment for any favours that he received,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6078,
            "text": "but only to seek the good pleasure of his Lord Most High.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6079,
            "text": "He will surely be well-pleased (with him).",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 93,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الضُّحَىٰ",
        "englishName": "Ad-Dhuhaa",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Morning Hours",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6080,
            "text": "By the bright forenoon,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6081,
            "text": "and by the night when it covers the world with peace:",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6082,
            "text": "(O Prophet), your Lord has neither forsaken you, nor is He displeased.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6083,
            "text": "Indeed what is to come will be better for you than what has gone by.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6084,
            "text": "Verily your Lord will soon give you so amply that you will be well-pleased.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6085,
            "text": "Did He not find you an orphan and then gave you shelter?",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6086,
            "text": "Did He not find you unaware of the Right Way, and then directed you to it?",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6087,
            "text": "And did He not find you in want, and then enriched you?",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6088,
            "text": "Therefore, be not harsh with the orphan;",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6089,
            "text": "and chide not him who asks,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6090,
            "text": "and proclaim the bounty of your Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 535,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 94,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الشَّرۡحِ",
        "englishName": "Ash-Sharh",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Consolation",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6091,
            "text": "(O Prophet), Did We not lay open your breast",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 536,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6092,
            "text": "and relieve you of the burden",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 536,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6093,
            "text": "that had well-nigh broken your back?",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 536,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6094,
            "text": "And did We not exalt your fame?",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 536,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6095,
            "text": "Indeed, there is ease with hardship.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 536,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6096,
            "text": "Most certainly, there is ease with hardship.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 596,
            "ruku": 536,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6097,
            "text": "So, whenever you are free, strive in devotion,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
