            "text": "By the fig and the olive;",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 537,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6100,
            "text": "and by the Mount Sinai,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 537,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6101,
            "text": "and by this city (of Makkah), a haven of peace:",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 537,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6102,
            "text": "surely We created man in the best mould;",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 537,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6103,
            "text": "then We reverted him to the lowest of the low,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 537,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6104,
            "text": "except those who have faith and do righteous deeds. Theirs is a never ending reward.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 537,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6105,
            "text": "Who, then, can give the lie to you, (O Prophet), about the Reward and the Punishment?",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 537,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6106,
            "text": "Is not Allah the Greatest of all sovereigns?",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 537,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 96,
        "name": "سُورَةُ العَلَقِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Alaq",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Clot",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6107,
            "text": "Recite in the name of your Lord Who created,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6108,
            "text": "created man from a clot of congealed blood.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6109,
            "text": "Recite: and your Lord is Most Generous,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6110,
            "text": "Who taught by the pen,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6111,
            "text": "taught man what he did not know.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6112,
            "text": "Nay, surely man transgresses;",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6113,
            "text": "for he believes himself to be self-sufficient.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6114,
            "text": "Surely to your Lord is your return.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6115,
            "text": "Did you see him who forbids",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6116,
            "text": "a servant (of Allah) when he prays?",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6117,
            "text": "Did you consider: what if he is on the Right Way,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6118,
            "text": "and enjoins piety?",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6119,
            "text": "Did you consider: what if he gives the lie (to the Truth) and turns away (from it)?",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6120,
            "text": "Does he not know that Allah sees everything?",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6121,
            "text": "No indeed; if he does not desist, We shall drag him by the forelock;",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6122,
            "text": "by the lying forelock steeped in sin.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6123,
            "text": "So let him summon his helpmates;",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6124,
            "text": "We too shall summon the guards of Hell.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6125,
            "text": "No, not at all. Never obey him. But prostrate yourself and become nigh (to your Lord).",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 597,
            "ruku": 538,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": {
              "id": 15,
              "recommended": false,
              "obligatory": true
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 97,
        "name": "سُورَةُ القَدۡرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Qadr",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Power, Fate",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6126,
            "text": "Behold, We revealed this (Qur'an) on the Night of Power.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 539,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6127,
            "text": "And what do you know what the Night of Power is?",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 539,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6128,
            "text": "The Night of Power is better than a thousand months.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 539,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6129,
            "text": "The angels along with the Spirit descend in it by the permission of their Lord with all kinds of decrees.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 539,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6130,
            "text": "All peace is that night until the rise of dawn.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 539,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 98,
        "name": "سُورَةُ البَيِّنَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Bayyina",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Evidence",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6131,
            "text": "Those who disbelieved – be they from the People of the Book or from those who associated others with Allah in His Divinity – will not desist from unbelief until the Clear Proof should come to them;",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 540,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6132,
            "text": "a Messenger from Allah, reciting from Purified Scrolls;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 540,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6133,
            "text": "in writings wherein are scriptures, absolutely true and unerring.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 540,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6134,
            "text": "Nor did those to whom the Book had been given split up until after the Proof (of the Right Way) had come to them.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 540,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6135,
            "text": "Yet all that they had been commanded was that they serve Allah, with utter sincerity, devoting themselves exclusively to Him, and that they establish Prayer and pay Zakah. That is the Right Faith.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 540,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6136,
            "text": "Those who disbelieved – be they from among the People of the Book or among those who associated others with Allah in His Divinity– shall be in the Fire, and will abide in it. They are the worst of creatures.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 540,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6137,
            "text": "But those that believe and work righteous deeds, they are the best of creatures.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 598,
            "ruku": 540,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6138,
            "text": "Their recompense lies with their Lord: Gardens of eternity beneath which rivers flow; therein they shall dwell, forever and ever. Allah is well-pleased with them, and they are well-pleased with Him. All this is for him who fears his Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 540,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 99,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الزَّلۡزَلَةِ",
        "englishName": "Az-Zalzala",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Earthquake",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6139,
            "text": "When the earth will be shaken with a mighty shaking,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 541,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6140,
            "text": "and the earth will throw up all her burdens,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 541,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6141,
            "text": "and man will cry out: “What is the matter with her?”",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 541,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6142,
            "text": "On that Day it will relate all her news,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 541,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6143,
            "text": "for your Lord will have commanded her (to do so).",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 541,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6144,
            "text": "On that Day people will go forth in varying states so that they be shown their deeds.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 541,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6145,
            "text": "So, whoever does an atom's weight of good shall see it;",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 541,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6146,
            "text": "and whoever does an atom's weight of evil shall see it.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 541,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 100,
        "name": "سُورَةُ العَادِيَاتِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Aadiyaat",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Chargers",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
