            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6149,
            "text": "then raid by the dawn,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6150,
            "text": "and blaze a trail of dust,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6151,
            "text": "and penetrate deep into a host.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6152,
            "text": "Verily man is most ungrateful to his Lord;",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6153,
            "text": "and he himself is a witness to that,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6154,
            "text": "and surely he loves riches with a passionate loving.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6155,
            "text": "Is he not aware that when whatever lies (buried) in the graves is overthrown;",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6156,
            "text": "and the secrets of the hearts are laid bare (and examined)?",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6157,
            "text": "Surely on that Day will their Lord be fully informed about them.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 101,
        "name": "سُورَةُ القَارِعَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Qaari'a",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Calamity",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6158,
            "text": "The Calamity!",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6159,
            "text": "What is the Calamity?",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6160,
            "text": "And what do you know what the Calamity is?",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6161,
            "text": "On that Day human beings shall be like scattered moths,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6162,
            "text": "and the mountains shall be like fluffs of carded wool in varying colours.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6163,
            "text": "Then he whose scales weigh heavier",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6164,
            "text": "shall have a blissful life;",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6165,
            "text": "but he whose scales weigh lighter,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6166,
            "text": "his shall be the deep pit for a dwelling.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6167,
            "text": "And what do you know what that is?",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6168,
            "text": "A Blazing Fire!",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 543,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 102,
        "name": "سُورَةُ التَّكَاثُرِ",
        "englishName": "At-Takaathur",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Competition",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6169,
            "text": "The craving for ever-greater worldly gains and to excel others in that regard keeps you occupied",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 544,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6170,
            "text": "until you reach your graves.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 544,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6171,
            "text": "Nay, you will soon come to know;",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 544,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6172,
            "text": "nay, again, you shall soon come to know.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 544,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6173,
            "text": "Nay, would that you knew with certainty of knowledge (what your attitude will lead to, you would never have acted the way you do).",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 544,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6174,
            "text": "You will surely end up seeing Hell;",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 544,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6175,
            "text": "again, you shall most certainly end up seeing it with absolute certainty.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 544,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6176,
            "text": "Then, on that Day, you will be called to account for all the bounties you enjoyed.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 600,
            "ruku": 544,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 103,
        "name": "سُورَةُ العَصۡرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Asr",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Declining Day, Epoch",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6177,
            "text": "By the time!",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 545,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6178,
            "text": "Lo! Man is in a state of loss;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 545,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6179,
            "text": "save those who have faith and do righteous deeds, and counsel each other to hold on to truth and counsel each other to be steadfast.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 545,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 104,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الهُمَزَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Humaza",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Traducer",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6180,
            "text": "Woe to every fault-finding backbiter;",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 546,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6181,
            "text": "who amasses wealth and counts it over and again.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 546,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6182,
            "text": "He thinks that his wealth will immortalise him forever.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 546,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6183,
            "text": "Nay, he shall be thrown into the Crusher.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 546,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6184,
            "text": "And what do you know what the Crusher is?",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 546,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6185,
            "text": "It is the Fire kindled by Allah,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 546,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6186,
            "text": "the Fire that shall rise to the hearts (of criminals).",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 546,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6187,
            "text": "Verily it will close in upon them,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 546,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6188,
            "text": "in outstretched columns.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 546,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 105,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الفِيلِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Fil",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Elephant",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6189,
            "text": "Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with the people of the elephants?",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 547,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6190,
            "text": "Did He not bring their plan to naught?",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 547,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6191,
            "text": "And He sent against them swarms of birds",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 547,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6192,
            "text": "which smote them with stones of baked clay,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 547,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6193,
            "text": "and made them like straw eaten up (by cattle).",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 601,
            "ruku": 547,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 106,
        "name": "سُورَةُ قُرَيۡشٍ",
        "englishName": "Quraish",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Quraysh",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6194,
            "text": "Since the Quraysh became accustomed,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 548,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6195,
            "text": "accustomed to the journey of winter and summer,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 548,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6196,
            "text": "therefore, let them worship the Lord of this House;",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 548,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6197,
            "text": "Who fed them against hunger, and secured them against fear.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 548,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 107,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المَاعُونِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Maa'un",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Almsgiving",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6198,
            "text": "Did you see him who gives the lie to the Reward and Punishment of the Hereafter?",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 549,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6199,
            "text": "Such is the one who repulses the orphans away,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 549,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6200,
            "text": "and urges not the feeding of the needy.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 549,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6201,
            "text": "Woe, then, to those who pray,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 549,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6202,
            "text": "but are heedless in their Prayers,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 549,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6203,
            "text": "those who do good (in order) to be seen,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 549,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6204,
            "text": "and deny people the articles of common necessity.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 549,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 108,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الكَوۡثَرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Kawthar",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Abundance",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6205,
            "text": "(O Prophet), We have surely bestowed upon you good in abundance.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 550,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6206,
            "text": "So offer Prayer and sacrifice to your Lord alone.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 550,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6207,
            "text": "Verily your enemy alone has been cut off from the roots.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 602,
            "ruku": 550,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 109,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الكَافِرُونَ",
        "englishName": "Al-Kaafiroon",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Disbelievers",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6208,
            "text": "Say: “O unbelievers!”",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 551,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6209,
            "text": "I do not worship those that you worship",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 551,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6210,
            "text": "neither do you worship Him Whom I worship;",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 551,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6211,
            "text": "nor will I worship those whom you have worshipped;",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 551,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6212,
            "text": "nor are you going to worship Him Whom I worship.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 551,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6213,
            "text": "To you is your religion, and to me, my religion.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 551,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 110,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النَّصۡرِ",
        "englishName": "An-Nasr",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Divine Support",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6214,
            "text": "When the help comes from Allah, and victory (is granted),",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 552,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6215,
            "text": "and you see people entering Allah's religion in multitudes,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 552,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6216,
            "text": "then extol the praise of your Lord and pray to Him for forgiveness. For He indeed is ever disposed to accept repentance.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 552,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 111,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المَسَدِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Masad",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Palm Fibre",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6217,
            "text": "Destroyed were the hands of Abu Lahab, and he lay utterly doomed.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 553,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6218,
            "text": "His wealth did not avail him, nor his acquisitions.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 553,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6219,
            "text": "Surely, he will be cast into a Flaming Fire",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 553,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6220,
            "text": "along with his wife, that carrier of slanderous tales;",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 553,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6221,
            "text": "upon her neck shall be a rope of palm-fibre.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 603,
            "ruku": 553,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 112,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الإِخۡلَاصِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Ikhlaas",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Sincerity",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6222,
            "text": "Say: “He is Allah, the One and Unique;",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 554,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6223,
            "text": "Allah, Who is in need of none and of Whom all are in need;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 554,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6224,
            "text": "He neither begot any nor was He begotten,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 554,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6225,
            "text": "and none is comparable to Him.”",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 554,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 113,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الفَلَقِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Falaq",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Dawn",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6226,
            "text": "Say: “I seek refuge with the Lord of the rising day;",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 555,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6227,
            "text": "from the evil of all that He created;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 555,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6228,
            "text": "from the evil of night's darkness when it spreads around;",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 555,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6229,
            "text": "from the evil of the women who blow on knots;",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 555,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6230,
            "text": "and from the evil of the envier when he envies.”",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 555,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 114,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النَّاسِ",
        "englishName": "An-Naas",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Mankind",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6231,
            "text": "Say: “I seek refuge with the Lord of mankind;",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 556,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6232,
            "text": "the King of mankind,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 604,
            "ruku": 556,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
